r scriptures view/expect it: Tagore is Jesus patibilis, \"the suffering form of primal man.\" all this signifies the completion of the task/purpose for which world was made in the first place: as a \"mechanism\" by which the swallowed light is progressively unmixed from the Darkness that swallowed it - as in my case in 2-3-74: this is consistently + purely Gnostic-Manichaean. + this is the dialectic revealed to me, this battle between light + dark ead my vision of Tagore been of the Christ who return in geory to judge + rule, it would C-189 have obviated the entire Gnostic-manichaean thrust (content) of my whole experience (gnosis), especially that of Valis, Jesus patibilis. two points: 1) in my ignorance (of my own avowed system, Gnosticism) I anticipated the orthodox 2nd advent of the N.T. 2) conversely, when I did receive the vision of Tagore it did in fact conform not to my expectations but to Gnosticism-manichaeism. These are very important points. stunning thought: hyperfield ab may be the how (means!) + the two coaxial worlds a and B that are 1800 mirror opposites of each other may be the what's (end!); that is, they can co-exist with all their sign-values reversed - in relation to each other. because of hyperfield Ab (\"eide\"). This is quite a different view; viz: if hyperfield Ab is regarded as truly real You have Platonist metaphysics (the Forms), but if you think of hyper field AB as how, as the means that permits two reverse coaxial worlds to co-exist, there Gnosticism is the case: A (USA 1974) is ostensible, the official world (view]; B is the Gnostic truth, the subversive protest world (view]; This coincides with my theory of two information-systems competing: the plasmate cooking + riding our communications media is at 180Â° variance to the ostensible message-traffic Thus all at once what seemed clearly to be Platonist meta C-190 physics last February is still the case but it is how you get the two coaxial worlds it is with them - + + specifically with the covert one that we are concerned. The hyperfield Ab is like a sine waves official world I e B Gnostic inversion. Thus there is an epistemological reality connected with the Gnostis that has to do with literal ontology, not just subjective viewpoint by the percipient. + this leads us back to the absolute ontology of the two mutually exclusive opposed categories of ignorance (ostensible official world A) + knowledge (covert \"protest\" world B). this insight one year after the coaxial worlds - common essence insight may be the 3rd true insight of this whole exegesis. Put another way, suppose two I advance the out so insight of mutually exclusive worlds, each 1800 reversed from the other, existing coaxially, at one (?) time + place - yet somehow at two times + two places in a lesser, merely seeming sense. One asks at once \"how can this be?\" it would seem not only impossible but even unintelligible. but the Feb '81 \"not 2 mothers but one mother twice\" meta-abstraction (noesis - of the eide) will account for it. C-19 what may be the most important element of this sine wave model is that it does grant absolute + 1800 opposed ontological bases to the two worlds + hence to the two Gnostic categories of ignorance + knowing, since world A is (1) effortlessly seen but (2) not (somehow) the case, + (3) world B is very difficult to see (a log nutive-perceptual occlusion must be lifted) + (4) somehow is the case. + yet both are now + both are here; the Paradigm is \"Tears\" which is not one text but two \"time-sharing\" texts fed along a common (unitary) carrier or signal: the novel itself. \"Tears proves it can be done because \"Tears\" Does it - moreover, for a time I was able to bifurcate (divine into set + ground) the two interwoven texts Thus (as I say ultra super) \"Tears\" exists in both worlds + hence is part of hyperfield AB. It seems quite evident - even fundamentally obvious that not all things are. the whole thing is: certain (but not all) objects serve care in) both worlds, A and B. + this is what I caught the Xtian Fish sign doing in 2-74: one object seen twice; i.e. in both worlds whereupon I leaped to the obvious + ineluctable conclusion that if one C-192 object served both worlds, ipso facto there had to be two worlds [somehow coaxial). All this analysis, then, is precisely applicable to 2-74; this is exactly what I realized: the one object (the Xtian Golden Fish sign) was in -seen in, served in - both worlds. + this is Gnosticism; this is really what it + its two mutually exclusive ontological categories are about. Thus 2-74 was Gnostic, had to do with what Gnosticism really pertains too If you discover that true secret Xtians exist this proves two things not one. 1) that true secret Xtian exist, so Xtianity is real. 2) the ostensible Xtians are not real Xtianss, hence here is where the sign reversal occurs. They are anti-Xtians, + from this you extrapolate to ostensible world as a whole (1) which is not what it seems to be but is 180 opposite. (2) a true secret real + good \"coaxial\" world really exists interphosed with it (somehow). the goal of it all is: that your death should emanate out of what you are ontologically, + not part - the ultimate parts- of the Geworfenheit imposed on you as heimarmene, i.e. to which you succeemb + must succumb this transformation occurs when you cease to run from your death, turn + face it + make it yous",
